      <h1 style="margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;">About this project</h1>
      <p style="color:#555; margin-top:0">
        This calculator estimates electricity bills in Kosovo using multi-group 2025 tariffs.
        Frontend is <strong>Astro + React</strong>; pricing logic lives in a shared <strong>TypeScript module</strong>;
        serverless API is a <strong>Netlify Function</strong>; tariffs are editable via JSON.
      </p>

      <h2>Highlights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Households (1-tariff & 2-tariff) with 0–800 kWh blocks.</li>
        <li>Business groups including demand/reactive (where applicable).</li>
        <li>JSON-driven tariffs → update prices without code changes.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>For estimation/education; official bills may differ.</li>
        <li>Update <code>src/data/tariffs_2025.json</code> if tariffs change.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:2rem;color:#666;">Last updated: {new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)}</p>
